# Phase 18: UI Refinements & Advanced Display

This phase focuses on polishing the projection display for better readability and optimizing the Bible search layout.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Song Wrapping Logic**: I will implement a "Smart Wrap" for songs. It will first try to keep one line per lyrics line. If the font shrinks below a threshold (e.g., 40pt), it will allow wrapping to prevent the text from becoming unreadably small.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Advanced Text Scaling Logic
- **[MODIFY] [projector_view.dart](file:///c:/Users/bhanu/projects/KeryxPro/lib/features/presentation/presentation/widgets/projector_view.dart)**:
    - Implement conditional `maxLines` and `wrapWords` logic.
    - **For Scripture**: Use `maxLines: 30` and `wrapWords: true` to prioritize readability and space utilization.
    - **For Songs**:
        - Use `maxLines: lineCount` initially to keep lines unbroken.
        - If the calculated `fontSize` would drop below a "comfort threshold" (e.g., 40), increase `maxLines` to `lineCount * 2` and enable wrapping.
    - Ensure `fontSize` never exceeds the preset value.

### 2. Scripture Enhancements
- **[MODIFY] [bible_search_tab.dart](file:///c:/Users/bhanu/projects/KeryxPro/lib/features/bible/presentation/widgets/bible_search_tab.dart)**:
